yses, (4) and finally, as a starting point for users to extend with reactions other than the OER, as part of a collaborative software community.</ce:para></abstract></dc:description><link href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/abstract/scopus_id/85152207686" rel="self"/><link href="https://www.scopus.com/inward/record.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&amp;scp=85152207686&amp;origin=inward" rel="scopus"/><link href="https://www.scopus.com/inward/citedby.uri?partnerID=HzOxMe3b&amp;scp=85152207686&amp;origin=inward" rel="scopus-citedby"/></coredata><affiliation id="60027950" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60027950"><affilname>Carnegie Mellon University</affilname><affiliation-city>Pittsburgh</affiliation-city><affiliation-country>United States</affiliation-country></affiliation><authors><author seq="1" auid="58151624800"><ce:initials>R.Y.</ce:initials><ce:indexed-name>Sanspeur R.Y.</ce:indexed-name><ce:surname>Sanspeur</ce:surname><ce:given-name>Rohan Yuri</ce:given-name><preferred-name><ce:initials>R.Y.</ce:initials><ce:indexed-name>Sanspeur R.Y.</ce:indexed-name><ce:surname>Sanspeur</ce:surname><ce:given-name>Rohan Yuri</ce:given-name></preferred-name><author-url>https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/58151624800</author-url><affiliation id="60027950" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60027950"/></author><author seq="2" auid="57204359851"><ce:initials>J.</ce:initials><ce:indexed-name>Heras-Domingo J.</ce:indexed-name><ce:surname>Heras-Domingo</ce:surname><ce:given-name>Javier</ce:given-name><preferred-name><ce:initials>J.</ce:initials><ce:indexed-name>Heras-Domingo J.</ce:indexed-name><ce:surname>Heras-Domingo</ce:surname><ce:given-name>Javier</ce:given-name></preferred-name><author-url>https://api.elsevier.com/content/author/author_id/57204359851</author-url><affiliation id="60027950" href="https://api.elsevier.com/content/affiliation/affiliation_id/60027950"/></author><author seq="3" auid="700421277